actions-and-tags-for-zotero.xpi
Automates tagging and workflow via custom scripts and event triggers (e.g., auto-tagging new items, auto-translating titles).
通过自定义脚本和事件触发（如新文献自动打标签、标题自动翻译）实现标签自动化与工作流优化。


zotero-style.xpi
Enhances UI with reading progress visualization, nested tag management, and journal metadata display, improving user experience.
通过阅读进度可视化、嵌套标签管理和期刊元数据显示增强用户界面，提升使用体验。
